{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Top Section (Full-width)
    
    Add a wrapper with the custom class: membership-hero-section
    
    Include the following fields as editable inputs in the section settings:
    
    Title (text)
    
    Subtitle (text)
    
    Description (rich text)
    
    Default values:
    
    Title: Choose Your Membership
    
    Subtitle: Unlock your path into the business of baseball
    
    Description:
    Join the world’s largest baseball business community with membership options built for students, professionals, and executives. Select the plan that fits your career goals.MEMBERSHIP CARD AREA (3 Columns)
    
    Container custom class: membership-pricing-wrapper
    Display 3 membership boxes side-by-side on desktop, stacked on mobile.
    
    Each Membership Card Should Include:
    
    Custom class for the card: membership-card
    
    Image/icon picker
    
    Membership Title (text)
    
    Short description (text)
    
    Price selector:
    
    Monthly Price (number)
    
    Yearly Price (number)
    
    Toggle switch on frontend to switch between monthly/yearly
    
    Feature list (repeatable field – 3–4 bullet items)
    
    CTA Button text (text)
    
    CTA Link (url)
    1. Basic Membership
    
    Title: Basic Member
    
    Description: Perfect for students and emerging professionals.
    
    Monthly Price: $0
    
    Yearly Price: $0
    
    Features:
    
    Access to community discussions
    
    Intro industry resources
    
    Career starter guidance
    
    Limited job board preview
    
    Button Text: Join Basic
    
    2. Premier Membership
    
    Title: Premier Member
    
    Description: For working professionals ready to grow in baseball.
    
    Monthly: $49
    
    Yearly: $499
    
    Features:
    
    Full job board access
    
    Exclusive content
    
    Monthly mentorship sessions
    
    Member discounts
    
    Button Text: Join Premier
    
    3. Elite Membership
    
    Title: Elite Member
    
    Description: The ultimate experience for serious baseball leaders.
    
    Monthly: $89
    
    Yearly: $899
    
    Features:
    
    Personalized mentorship
    
    VIP industry events
    
    Executive network access
    
    Premium resources & insights
    
    Button Text: Join Elite
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
